        <div id="q3" class="page">
          <div class="bg">
            <div class="mid_tit">
              <span lang="y" class="q-num">문제</span>
              <span lang="y" class="txt">몫의 크기를 비교하여 빈칸에 >, =, < 중 알맞은 것을 옮겨 보세요.</span>
            </div>
            <div class="qe_area">
              <div class="qe">
                <ul class="matching-pairs">
                  <li>
                    <span lang="y" class="txt">36÷8</span>
                    <span class="drag_circle droppable center" data-answer="크다"></span>
                    <span lang="y" class="txt">15÷6</span>
